===Noun===
'''heme''' (''[[uncountable]]'')
# The [[component]] of [[hemoglobin]] responsible for [[bind]]ing [[oxygen]], consists of an [[iron]] [[ion]] that binds oxygen and a [[porphyrin]] [[ring]] that binds the [[globin]] [[molecule]]s; one molecule binds one molecule of oxygen.

